  <p>Calls all of the <link xref="GLib.Hook"/> functions in a <link xref="GLib.HookList"/>.
Any function which returns <code>false</code> is removed from the <link xref="GLib.HookList"/>.</p>

<terms>
<item>
<title><code>may_recurse</code></title>
  <p><code>true</code> if functions which are already running
    (e.g. in another thread) can be called. If set to <code>false</code>,
    these are skipped</p>
